%T A393737 24897777178
%N A393737 Number of free polyominoes in the {7,7} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393737 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2). In this case, p=7, q=7 and P{p,oo} = A005419.
%Y A393737 Cf. A333018, A393734, A393735, A393736, A393738, A005419.
